  <front>
    <title>The FNV Non-Cryptographic Hash Algorithm</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-eastlake-fnv-09"/>
    <author initials="G." surname="Fowler" fullname="Glenn Fowler"/>
    <author initials="L. C." surname="Noll" fullname="Landon Curt Noll"/>
    <author initials="K." surname="Vo" fullname="Kiem-Phong Vo"/>
    <author initials="D. E." surname="Eastlake" fullname="Donald E. Eastlake 3rd"/>
    <date day="05" month="April" year="2015"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>FNV (Fowler/Noll/Vo) is a fast, non-cryptographic hash algorithm with
   good dispersion. The purpose of this document is to make information
   on FNV and open source code performing FNV conveniently available to
   the Internet community.</t>
    </abstract>
